  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Psychiatric rehabilitation for farmers in distress</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">This project aims to aid farmer&apos;s in depression, their relatives and others struggling with mental health problems in Vidarbha region. Initiating rehabilitation and counselling centre with face-to-face treatment for patients may help to reduce the farmer&apos;s suicide crisis in Vidarbha. This project may help to tackle several problems including; lack of treatment, lack of resources and facilities for the mentally ill and social discrimination against those suffering depression problems.</narrative>
  </description>
